Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花语意味深长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌曲 杀意都跨越时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.76,0:00:21.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,35)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}正因为你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.87,0:00:30.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}喜好不同 脚程与表达的方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.37,0:00:37.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}如今我们在两人的记忆中正在渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.31,0:00:45.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(60,0)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我摸索过 却开始探寻其他人与未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:52.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我比自己想象的活得更坚强 追寻一种特别的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}为难以应付的每一天所苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.37,0:00:59.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx129}ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.59,0:01:06.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}为了不再迷惑 请别松开你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(30,40)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}即使是互相伤害的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:21.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我只是一直在迷惘的时空中找寻答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.59,0:01:27.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}朝着下一个舞台  {\fscx132}you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,800)}{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:39.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(0,730)}{\fs20}{\fscx101}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们受加那娱乐集团会长加那善则之托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出席晚会并保护她的妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(485,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她近来受到什么人的骚扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.32,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚会中途 突然停电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美咲在她自己的房间里被人袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(196,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都怀疑犯人就是晚会的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.97,0:02:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰拉尔天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.07,0:02:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧接着杰拉尔天马就被人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色杀意的夜想曲（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凶器是骑士的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴调音用的音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个伤痕是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 琴凳为什么在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压在大沙发下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要到处乱走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诸位 为了保护现场请大家都去休憩室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,善则先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀害天马的是你么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在休憩室 就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天马根本不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人走到钢琴那边去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法 我正想在这坐下的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.62,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到“嘶”的响声和惨叫 跑过去一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天马已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是当时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的人都在一楼大厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真够呛 你干了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.12,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说了 不是我干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从一开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我独断决定的这件事 你心里就觉得不满意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才你又得知 天马和嫂子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前恋爱过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就激动起来了 不是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在他就是支持你也晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真遗憾 会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在 控制加那娱乐集团的变成谁了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看见犯人了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到这里来的时候已经空无一人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才美咲带我们来参观的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(259,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴盖是盖着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杰拉尔打开的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以这个房间的大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不打开盖 琴声也足够响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰拉尔没有必要打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天马进这个房间之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴的盖子是打开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以这样设想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.87,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人在杀人时 为了让别人从这边看不到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以预先把盖子打开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个房间的出口只有通往休憩室的那扇门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窗户虽然开了一扇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是下面是海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是跳下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也很难避开礁石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个窗台上也有伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是被绳子之类的东西勒过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美咲被袭击的时候留下的痕迹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(197,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有根绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从上从下都可以逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有这种可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是能在这么短的时间内逃走么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地板上留下的剑尖的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.05,0:05:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是垂直于地面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整理一下案发当时各位所在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诸位请去隔壁的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边这个小吊灯的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比那边那个大吊灯的位置高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美咲带我们来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(259,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是在更低的位置上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里也有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和窗台上的痕迹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调节吊灯高低的就是这个手柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很容易就可以转动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这个盒子上没有灰尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红色爱的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那首歌是10年前天马送给美咲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(472,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这样的话就怎么样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是血么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢琴的里面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小林警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警部说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我去找贝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是在海里么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何 善则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请跟我回警署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要说多少遍你才会相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美咲 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(303,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果和那个地方对得上的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这里掉下来的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那个装饰品的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人只可能是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公司我会照应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.71,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是要赶紧出个杰拉尔天马的追悼版吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个就是袭击美咲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(396,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如你所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下面的海岸上找到了贝多芬像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没叫你去找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扶手下面留有好像是细绳之类的勒出来的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.06,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是什么线啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是钓鱼的时候用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鱼线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.88,0:09:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.88,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个雕像上还带着鱼线和这个棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扶手上的伤痕是鱼线勒出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推理的不错 就这么继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 为什么用贝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 这上面也有贝多芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在这房间偷拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正好是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 贝多芬像没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿披风的外国人是怎么来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.60,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贝多芬就是这个房间里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要做这个机关的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得那里的宽度应该和棒的长度相同么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.43,0:10:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那里缺的一块就是刚才的碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那边的阳台上试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美咲 有鱼竿的话借我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(202,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阳台的顶棚比扶手向外伸的更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鱼竿就简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把线的一头系成环 上面缀个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是为了穿过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绳子穿过扶手下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小林警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿着鱼线的环 把手指伸进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.19,0:10:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警部能不能把大衣借我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小林警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和犯人扭打 按照我的指示放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在放手 拉绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 完美极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情景和美咲被袭击的时候一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(272,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 嫂子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的房间里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着就象穿披风的外国人逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 加害者和被害者就是同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.47,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拉掉楼下的电闸 立刻跑进房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁上门开始呼救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(390,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(334,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推理的很出色 不愧是名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.77,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那些骚扰 恐吓信都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是希望你能相信 所以才演了这么一出戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这个事和天马被杀没有直接关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善则 请跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么下去可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是钢琴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.07,0:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部 先别把他带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.17,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要做推理演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 警部 我终于弄明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你看看地板上的那个伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕的角度是垂直于地面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查的结果也是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.47,0:13:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 窗台和回廊的扶手上的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马手上拿的音叉上的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些伤痕联系起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就构成了一个非常恐怖的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地板上的伤痕的正上方有个吊灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.47,0:13:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吊灯也就是连接这些伤痕的最后一环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难 难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊在那个吊灯上的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.97,0:13:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂直的掉落下来 穿透天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.17,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在地板上留下了垂直地面的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.47,0:13:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他正巧站在剑落下的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑也应该是刺在头上或者肩上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.87,0:14:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天马当时是脸朝下的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是这个姿势呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音叉可以解开这个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有琴凳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.27,0:14:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴和琴凳之间的距离只有一人宽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马走到琴键前面准备弹琴的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现琴凳倒在钢琴边上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且调音用的音叉也掉在地上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 天马就去捡音叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 这样的话就是背对着剑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是那个捡起来的音叉使剑落下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个恐怖的机关是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把剑挂在长绳的中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.07,0:15:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个绳头一起穿过吊灯的轮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再绕过回廊的扶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头在大沙发上绕几圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线头系在音叉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一头 从窗户扔出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面悬挂着重物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 只要等天马去捡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压在椅子腿下面的音叉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑的重量使音叉上系的绳被拉脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重的剑就在一瞬间落下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 系在剑上的鱼线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被窗外挂着的重物拉着落下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就消失在海里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么犯人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.12,0:15:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回想一下 使用鱼线做的机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用重物将证据带入大海的这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才那个穿披风的外国人的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是非常相像么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(348,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 犯人就是你 美咲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(422,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在给所有人倒上酒之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.07,0:16:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作是去了厨房 其实是在这里做手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吊灯吊到最高点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样剑就不容易被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还能够提高杀伤力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来认为你是名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是徒有虚名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据证明是我做的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 请看看钢琴的盖子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和里面沾上的污渍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒沾在钢琴的那个位置上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明是在打开盖的时候掉落在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够让酒掉在那里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么肯定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.57,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为米歇尔从法国带来的酒是独一无二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这就是我的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.27,0:17:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那酒大家都喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没喝的只有你 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(414,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心撞到你 把酒洒在你身上的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是当时留在你胸花上的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.47,0:17:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你打开钢琴盖的时候掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.27,0:17:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了很多假象伪装天马骚扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把旧照片放在容易被发现的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以激起善则的怒气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让他替你担起杀害天马的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 是真的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(277,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你怎么解释刚才有人袭击她的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.27,0:18:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她自导自演的戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个恐吓电话也是美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn宋体}{\fs28}{\pos(433,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的从自己的手机上给自己打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫂子为什么要杀天马呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才找到的天马和美咲的照片上的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(359,471)}{\shad1}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美咲结婚短短半年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(259,471)}{\shad1}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 红色爱的夜想曲也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.87,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前天马送给你的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌看上去像是首情歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 根据花语来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红玫瑰代表热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金盏花代表绝望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半边莲代表恶意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大理花代表背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 这首歌表达的其实是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对背叛自己的爱人的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么 美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(403,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 10年前的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说无论如何都无法离开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他约到附近的海岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他推了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.47,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你就和善则结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天马因为你的绝情而受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远走海外 获得成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你知道了杰拉尔天马的真面目之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.97,0:19:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了隐藏你过去所犯下的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有再一次杀掉天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你为什么要把罪名转嫁给善则呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是昌代的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司和丈夫就都被她夺走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.07,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她夺不走监狱里的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护着公司等我丈夫回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体}{\fs28}{\pos(347,471)}{\b1}咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.27,0:20:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前没有找到天马的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是他还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直为此担惊受怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也明白那首歌的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实杰拉尔在音乐会上唱这首歌的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.02,0:20:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都轻声说一句法语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译成日文就是为了挽救你那受伤的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在重新修改的歌词里换了花的种类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能就是这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了红玫瑰以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的分别改成了芦荟 火炎花和橄榄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花语是悲哀 和平和光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.17,0:20:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马知道你可能作为杀人犯而被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然怀着苦涩的回忆继续唱这首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.97,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特地和加那集团签约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.47,0:21:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然曾经一度沉浸在悲痛之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他已经不再记恨你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己也在事业上取得成功 非常幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想让你听听真正意义的红色爱的夜想曲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.03,0:21:48.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}要用什么方式传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:55.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}才能让你明白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.42,0:22:04.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}{\fad(60,0)}自从那次之后  不知多少个季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}就这样过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}总是笑着守候在我身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.03,0:22:28.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}你不敢告诉我的事情 还有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.53,0:22:33.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx129}Secret of my heart  {\fscx107}{\fscy95}并不是怀疑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.49,0:22:39.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}不管何时  只要还有少许的未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:44.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}真相一定会落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.64,0:22:51.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}{\fscx107}{\fscy95}我无法再说什么 只有继续等待机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.52,0:22:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.57,0:23:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那开始就对花语入迷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 园子 ByeBye
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.97,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 路上经过花店买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.47,0:23:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.97,0:23:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.57,0:23:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的桃花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.77,0:23:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花语是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天 下 无 敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.67,0:23:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.87,0:23:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下无敌是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.37,0:23:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.27,0:23:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在他们等电梯这会儿跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.57,0:24:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.97,0:24:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是 你是个冒充的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.07,0:24:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九个门的大搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.07,0:24:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.67,0:24:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉丁字母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.62,0:24:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是在9层的高级公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探团大活跃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.67,0:24:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的出场呢